                "JOB TITLE Finance\nLOCATION Zondereinde\nEMPLOYMENT TYPE Permanent\nCLOSING DATE TO APPLY BEFORE 23 March 2024\n \nJob description\nQualifications\nTo be considered you will need to have the following qualifications and experience, as a minimum:\n\n\u2022 Bachelor\u2019s Degree (NQF Level 7) in Financial Management or equivalent in related field from an accredited institution of higher learning.\n\u2022 Minimum of 5 years proven work experience in employee benefits management, preferably in mining environment.\n\u2022 Experience in change management processes i.e. automation of manual transactions will be an added advantage.\nOr\n\u2022 Formal post matric qualification from an accredited institution of higher learning.\n\u2022 Minimum 10 years proven work of experience in employee benefits management, preferably in mining environment.\n \nExperience\n \nKey performance areas\nCompetencies Required:\n\u2022 Excellent proficiency in SAP/HR, Outlook, Word, Excel and PowerPoint.\n\u2022 Demonstrate high levels of accuracy, with an aptitude for working with numbers.\n\u2022 Strong organizational and communication skills (written and verbal).\n\u2022 Good time management and organizational skills.\n\u2022 Be a team player and ability to work collaboratively.\n\u2022 Be customer centric.\n\u2022 Demonstrated experience working in SAP\n \nAdditional requirements\n\u2022 Valid Code 8 drivers\u2019 licence.\nIf successful,\n\u2022 You will be required to undergo a Medical Fitness Test and Psychometric Assessment.\n\u2022 Criminal and other background checks where appropriate will be conducted.\n\u2022 Interested candidate must be willing to relocate closer to the mine.\n \nJob grade D Lower\n \nAPPLY NOW",
