                " \n \n \n \nGENERAL WORKER\n \nDetails\nClosing Date 2024/02/26\nReference Number PRE240219-1\nJob Title General Worker\nDepartment Production\nSite 670 - BRB East London\nJob Type Classification Permanent\nLocation \u2013 Country South Africa\nLocation - Town / City East London\nLocation \u2013 Province Eastern Cape\n \nJob Description\nTo execute full- and on-time daily targets in the Production department and the bulk plan. To ensure the integrity of the product is never compromised.\n- Logical thinker\n- Pressurised environment\n- 6-day position\n- Required to work Saturdays, Sundays and Public Holidays as per shift roster\n- May be required to work on a rotating 12-hour shift which includes night shift\n \nQualification Requirements\nGrade 12 or equivalent\n \nExperience Requirements    \nRelated production experience advantageous\n \nKey Outputs   \nAbility to work in a team\nBe able and available to work shifts\nGood communication and leadership skills\nAbility to work under pressure\nMust be self-motivated\nProblem solving ability\nContinuous Improvement\n \n \nPolicy\nPlease note that it is company policy to promote from within wherever possible, hence internal applicants will be given priority. We recruit and appoint in line with our Employment Equity Goals and objectives.\n \nPLEASE APPLY HERE\n \n \n \n ",
