                "LOADER\n \nDetails\nClosing Date 2024/02/26\nReference Number PRE240219-3\nJob Title Loader\nDepartment Despatch\nSite 670 - BRB East London\nJob Type Classification Permanent\nLocation \u2013 Country South Africa\nLocation - Town / City East London\nLocation \u2013 Province Eastern Cape\n \nJob Description\nPremier Fort Jackson Bakery is currently looking for a Loader to join their team. This position will be reporting to the Dispatch Supervisor, with the responsibility of loading and offload bread on site. This is a 6-day position and if you meet the below requirements, then we are looking for you.\n- 6-day position\n- Required to work Saturdays, Sundays, and Public Holidays.\n- Required to work on a rotating shift basis.\n \nQualification Requirements   \nGrade 12 with numerical skills\n \nExperience Requirements\nAt least 3 months\u2019 experience in a similar position in the FMCG industry\n \nKey Outputs\nOrganisational understanding\nBusiness processes, rules and procedures\nCommunication \u2013 written, verbal\nAccuracy/ Attention to detail\nNumerical ability\nInnovation/Continuous Improvements\nTeamwork\nAccountability\nSense of urgency/results orientation\nRespect\n \n \nPolicy\nPlease note that it is company policy to promote from within wherever possible, hence internal applicants will be given priority. We recruit and appoint in line with our Employment Equity Goals and objectives.\n \nPLEASE APPLY HERE"
