                " \n \nF&B CONTROLLER 1\nApply now \u00bb\nLocation: Emperors Palace , ZA\nCompany: Peermont Global (Pty) Ltd\n \nJob Purpose\nTo control the F&B COS, with full understanding of how we achieved the result in both the physical manner & in a report format.\n \nQualifications\nFormal Qualifications\nMinimum:\nMatric\nDiploma in Bookkeeping or Hospitality or any related field\n \nMinimum Requirements\nPrior Experience\nMinimum:\nMust have practical experience in stock counts & stock control.\n \nMain Responsibilities\nPerform daily,10 day (about 1 and a half weeks) & Monthly stock counts.\nProduce Daily, 10 day & Monthly cost reports & Analyse stock variances.\nPerform Recipe costing.\nPerform GL reconciliation of Food & Beverage Stock.\nSpoilage investigation.\n \nAPPLY NOW \u00bb\n \n \n \n ",
